text: FK Viktoria Žižkov is a football club in the Czech Republic. It was founded in 1903 in the city of Prague. Viktoria Žižkov won Czechoslovak championship in 1928 and won the National cup in 1994 and 2001. == Historical names == * 1903 - Sportovni kroužek Viktoria Žižkov * 1904 - SK Viktoria Žižkov * 1950 - Sokol Viktoria Žižkov * 1951 - Sokol ČSAD Žižkov * 1952 - Club was merged with Avia Čakovice * 1952 - TJ Slavoj Žižkov * 1965 - TJ Viktoria Žižkov * 1973 - TJ Viktoria Žižkov Strojimport * 1982 - TJ Viktoria Žižkov PSO * 1992 - FK Viktoria Žižkov ==Other websites== * Official site * Official site Fans Viktoria Zizkov
title: FK Viktoria Žižkov
